00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:58.240
its translation in English. I want you

00:01:54.960 --> 00:02:01.600
to pay uh pay close attention to things

00:01:58.240 --> 00:02:03.840
that are making this fixed bottleneck

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:05.920
assumption more challenging. For

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:09.679
